PHOTOGENICS 4 CD-ROM (ENGLISH VERSION) HAS BEEN RELEASED!
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE

Photogenics 4 CD-ROM has been released!
Suggested Retail Price DM 179.00
